                <L n="variations">
                  <T>0xDB3A817D<!--Tarot cards are a lucky find and for sure take some exploring to collect. I hear that collecting the last card requires a brush with Death! Come find me at the Thinned Festiveil for a free reading anytime. I love having a chance to show off my Tarot deck and my tarot-reading prowess.--></T>
                  <T>0x389439C2<!--I think the biggest indicator that I'm Macabre is that I love, love, love rainy days but can't really stand being in the sun that much. It's not that I hate the outdoors, not at all! I just try to pay attention to the weird little things out there, and rainy days are just, well, a bit weirder to me.--></T>
                  <T>0x6F194C65<!--I've been talking to Nyon more lately, but his soon-to-be-stepdad is a real enigma. I mean, everyone knows the rumors about Olive. You've seen the headstones, right? You know, from her other husbands? Come on, does Layne look like he's someone who misses a beat? Ew, no pun intended. --></T>
