            <V n="text" t="variation">
              <U n="variation">
                <L n="variations">
                  <T>0x267B1808<!--I try not to think a ton about how my parents even work, really. I mean, my mom was basically a ghost for a super, super long time. My dad's always talking about how he must have lived past lives or something, given how he's always got this Deja Vu thing going. You know how people talk about "old souls"? I think my parents are like that, though they're totally different personality-wise. --></T>
                  <T>0x20E74D83<!--Name-dropping is so passé, I know, but I can't help myself. Imagine getting super, super into something only to find out that the Sim who does it best is literally related to you! Right, so, once I got into Tarot and found out that collecting a whole deck summons this Lady Ravendancer Goth, I was all in. Then I find out about some Sim named Lolita Goth, and I guess we're related somehow on mom's side of the family and all that. Can't even wrap my mind around it, right? I've heard so much totally weird gossip about our families from summoning her and talking to her.--></T>
                  <T>0x236B252C<!--I suppose my whole morbid-fascination-with-Ghosts thing kicked off after finding out about tarot and about my distant ancestor, but I've always found ghosts really compelling. I want to know everything I possibly can. Did you know my relative, Esther, is the same way—and xie is a ghost already. I guess you can never know too much about those who have passed on, can you?--></T>
